        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2026-05-06T14:41:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution congratulates the people of Greece as they celebrate the 205th anniversary of the War of Greek Independence. The resolution also expresses support for the principles of democracy, human rights, and the rule of law to which the people of the United States and Greece are committed.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
